   Outgoing Mayor Edward I. Koch announced Thursday
he'll join WNEW-AM this January so he can continue to give New
Yorkers a piece of his mind five days a week.
   Koch, whose term ends Dec. 31, will provide a daily spot taking
``a light and humorous look at life in New York,'' said WNEW-AM
