<HEAD>Leader Says No Immediate Plans For Civilian Rule</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LAGOS, Nigeria (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Ghana's 7-year-old military government
will turn power over to civilians someday, but not soon, a member
of the ruling Provisional Defense Council said Thursday on a visit
to Lagos.
   ``We don't have plans on paper for a return to civil rule like
you have here in Nigeria, but our policies and plans are directed
